    "body": "From the discussion in https://github.com/bitcoin/bips/pull/2106#issuecomment-3961384931, this PR adds a warning to the \"if no matches are found, stop\" scanning step. Without it, wallet developers may be tempted to apply policy filtering (e.g. dust) before deciding to continue, causing subsequent outputs for the same sender to be missed.",
